{"tid":1473134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時代轉變 現在只有雞蛋與鐵蛋之別  共同嘅敵人永遠都會係高牆。","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T18:23:39.000Z","uid":166222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79e059f2dc196ebf6a4804ef05ea34330d9762e8","tid":1473134,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"好多人講 <br />\n雞蛋與高牆 誰是誰非<br />\n我仍會企係雞蛋依一邊。<br />\n<br />\n但社會進步得太快。<br />\n我地根本無喘息嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n所以 <br />\n依家基本上只有<br />\n雞蛋與鐵蛋之別 <br />\n<br />\n你問我選擇係咩？<br />\n我會同你講 <br />\n我會企係鐵蛋依一邊 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永不割席！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由始到終 我都會堅守三大原則 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不指責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟 手足 一個都不能少！！<br />\n一日未完 一日未都輸啊！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd33f0983aefe6f51f227fdb703f2da9e899aefd","tid":1473134,"uid":166222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔撚會割席！！！！"},{"pid":"d78afafdb5e6426bc527c4d83c0e6cf848e3925f","tid":1473134,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:16:36.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔撚會割席！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c37f908c742df0e69b1cc8cbfb9c9fd0cd7c2b1","tid":1473134,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d383d85a32f8c38e71947ae16758baa25b31309","tid":1473134,"uid":256594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"喂，依個post好正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8023a7832017ebec5207cab11fb81c460c31738","tid":1473134,"uid":166222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:20:28.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔撚會